{"tid":1661203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邱騰華：個別國家試圖透過單方面措施影響香港經貿地位是多此一舉","createTime":"2019-10-18T03:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T03:56:31.000Z","uid":97944,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"1b3b2f9bd207ea055ca5bac3ba0c96448c98b565","tid":1661203,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T03:06:25.000Z","msg":"【邱騰華：個別國家試圖透過單方面措施影響香港經貿地位是多此一舉】<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華出席一個電台節目後，回應美國眾議院通過《香港人權民主法案》，指如果某些國家用單方面措施試圖影響香港關稅地位或自主貿易政策，是多此一舉。他解釋香港不是與單一國家進行貿易，因此無論其他國家多大多有影響力，也不會影響到香港對外的多邊貿易關係。<br />\n<br />\nSource: 香港電台視像新聞 RTHK VNEWS"},{"pid":"64e01e6670c1417674e9b0e2941ac429584a4e6a","tid":1661203,"uid":208452,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T03:07:04.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係呀,我知我地講近廢話,但前線的確需要支援</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1655137/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1655137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書<br />\n<br />\n睇得自己咁高"},{"pid":"1be0e9e91400e0d441d5f7d8a6fe10d8dbf9784b","tid":1661203,"uid":274435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T03:08:23.000Z","msg":"有咩國家唔係睇美國頭"},{"pid":"de953cc0014ec73b628c9ea28e90b34e9e1dfcc3","tid":1661203,"uid":97944,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T03:20:59.000Z","msg":"香港口交部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6aaaf00f7e62a7fc89c7d98502172f7d437e285","tid":1661203,"uid":299694,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T03:22:04.000Z","msg":"笑左，唔講野冇人當你啞架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi